'''''Floran''''' was an [[CR92a Assassin-class corvette|''Assassin''-class corvettes]] belonging to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]]. They was supposed to rendezvous with the [[Alliance Fleet/Legends|Rebel Fleet]] at [[Sullust/Legends|Sullust]] but were destroyed by [[Maarek Stele/Legends|Maarek Stele]].

